divs: Sighting DetailsIt was 3:00am. and I was watching t.v. in my living room. Ihappened to look outof my window,the curtains were open, and I saw a helicopter hovering 100 feetfrom my window,which was elevated 20 feet. I noticed the spheres dart past 3feet from my window, trailing white sparks,not fire like,just white. They cameback and hovered 3 feet from my window, then quickly, but smoothly took off,trailing orange sparks.
